<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>BMR <%= @batch_ref %></title>
<style>
  @page { size: A4; margin: 16mm 12mm; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { font: 10pt/1.4 -apple-system, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; color: #111; margin: 0; }
  header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; border-bottom: 2px solid #111; padding-bottom: 10px; }
  .from { max-width: 55%; }
  .from h1 { font-size: 12pt; margin: 0 0 4px 0; }
  .from .meta { font-size: 9pt; color: #444; white-space: pre-line; }
  .doc-block { text-align: right; }
  .doc-block h2 { font-size: 16pt; margin: 0; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .doc-block .code { font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; font-size: 11pt; }
  .doc-block .brcgs { display: inline-block; margin-top: 4px; padding: 2px 6px; font-size: 8pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px; border: 1px solid #6ea1c8; color: #285a83; background: #eaf3fa; border-radius: 3px; }

  section { margin-top: 14px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
  h3.section-title { font-size: 9pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.7px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 3px; }

  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 6px; }
  .grid .cell { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 5px 7px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 9pt; }
  .grid .label { color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 7.5pt; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .grid .value { font-weight: 600; margin-top: 2px; }
  .grid .value.mono { font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 9pt; margin-top: 4px; }
  table th, table td { padding: 5px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; vertical-align: top; }
  table thead th { background: #f4f4f4; text-align: left; font-size: 8pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px; color: #555; border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc; }
  table td.num, table th.num { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; }
  .mono { font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; font-size: 9pt; }
  .muted { color: #666; }
  .empty-row td { color: #999; font-style: italic; text-align: center; }

  .signoff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 8px; }
  .signoff { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; border-radius: 3px; min-height: 62px; }
  .signoff .role { color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 7.5pt; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .signoff .name { font-weight: 600; margin-top: 3px; }
  .signoff .when { color: #666; font-size: 8pt; margin-top: 2px; }
  .signoff.blank { border-style: dashed; color: #999; }

  footer { margin-top: 22px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 8px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 8pt; color: #777; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="from">
    <h1><%= @company.name || "Company" %></h1>
    <div class="meta"><%= @company.legal_address || "" %><%= if @company.tax_number, do: "\nVAT " <> @company.tax_number, else: "" %><%= if @company.registration_number, do: "\nReg " <> @company.registration_number, else: "" %></div>
  </div>
  <div class="doc-block">
    <h2>Batch Manufacturing Record</h2>
    <div class="code"><%= @batch_ref %></div>
    <div class="brcgs">BRCGS Issue 9 · § 3.9 Traceability · § 5.6 Positive Release</div>
    <div style="margin-top: 4px; font-size: 8.5pt; color: #444;">Printed <%= @now %></div>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">Batch identity</h3>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">Product</div><div class="value"><%= @product_name %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">Item type</div><div class="value"><%= @product_type %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">Lot code</div><div class="value mono"><%= @lot_code %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">MO code</div><div class="value mono"><%= @mo_code %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">Batch qty</div><div class="value mono"><%= @batch_qty %> <%= @batch_uom %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">BOM revision</div><div class="value mono"><%= @bom_ref %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">Manufactured</div><div class="value"><%= @manufactured_at %></div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="label">Expiry</div><div class="value"><%= @expiry_at %></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">Production route — <%= length(@mo_chain) %> MO<%= if length(@mo_chain) == 1, do: "", else: "s" %> in order</h3>
  <p style="font-size: 8.5pt; color: #666; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
    Each MO below feeds the next: children (raw → semi) first, packaging / final assembly last. BRCGS Issue 9 § 3.9 traceability.
  </p>

  <%= for {section, idx} <- Enum.with_index(@mo_chain, 1) do %>
    <div style="border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 3px; padding: 8px; margin-top: 8px;">
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 6px;">
        <div>
          <span style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; font-weight: 600;">Step <%= idx %> · <%= section.code %></span>
          <span style="font-size: 8.5pt; color: #666; margin-left: 6px;"><%= section.role_label %></span>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size: 8pt; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555;"><%= section.status %></span>
      </div>

      <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); margin-bottom: 6px;">
        <div class="cell"><div class="label">Output item</div><div class="value"><%= section.output_item %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="label">Quantity</div><div class="value mono"><%= section.quantity %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="label">Chain position</div><div class="value" style="font-size: 8.5pt;"><%= section.parent_ref %></div></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="label">Planned window</div><div class="value" style="font-size: 8pt; color: #444;"><%= section.planned_window %></div></div>
        <div class="cell" style="grid-column: span 2;"><div class="label">Actual window</div><div class="value" style="font-size: 8pt; color: #444;"><%= section.actual_window %></div></div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 7.5pt; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin: 8px 0 2px 0;">Materials consumed</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width: 24px;">#</th>
            <th>Material</th>
            <th>Lot code</th>
            <th>Supplier batch</th>
            <th class="num">Booked</th>
            <th class="num">Consumed</th>
            <th>Picked by</th>
            <th>Closed by</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <%= if section.materials == [] do %>
            <tr class="empty-row"><td colspan="8">No bookings recorded against this MO.</td></tr>
          <% else %>
            <%= for {m, midx} <- Enum.with_index(section.materials, 1) do %>
              <tr>
                <td class="num"><%= midx %></td>
                <td><%= m.item_name %></td>
                <td class="mono"><%= m.lot_code %></td>
                <td class="mono"><%= m.supplier_batch %></td>
                <td class="num"><%= m.booked_qty %></td>
                <td class="num"><%= m.consumed_qty %></td>
                <td><%= m.picked_by %></td>
                <td><%= m.consumed_by %></td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p style="font-size: 7.5pt; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin: 8px 0 2px 0;">Routing operations</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width: 24px;">#</th>
            <th>Operation</th>
            <th>Workstation</th>
            <th>Planned</th>
            <th>Actual</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <%= if section.operations == [] do %>
            <tr class="empty-row"><td colspan="5">No routing operations logged.</td></tr>
          <% else %>
            <%= for {op, oidx} <- Enum.with_index(section.operations, 1) do %>
              <tr>
                <td class="num"><%= oidx %></td>
                <td><%= op.description %></td>
                <td><%= op.workstation %></td>
                <td class="muted"><%= op.planned_window %></td>
                <td class="muted"><%= op.actual_window %></td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p style="font-size: 7.5pt; color: #666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin: 8px 0 2px 0;">Output lots from this step</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width: 24px;">#</th>
            <th>Lot code</th>
            <th>Supplier batch</th>
            <th class="num">Qty received</th>
            <th>Status</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <%= if section.output_lots == [] do %>
            <tr class="empty-row"><td colspan="5">No output lots.</td></tr>
          <% else %>
            <%= for {ol, olidx} <- Enum.with_index(section.output_lots, 1) do %>
              <tr>
                <td class="num"><%= olidx %></td>
                <td class="mono"><%= ol.lot_code %></td>
                <td class="mono"><%= ol.supplier_batch %></td>
                <td class="num"><%= ol.qty %></td>
                <td><%= ol.status %></td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>

    </div>
  <% end %>
</section>

<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">Final output (top-of-tree)</h3>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width: 24px;">#</th>
        <th>Lot code</th>
        <th>Supplier batch</th>
        <th class="num">Qty received</th>
        <th>Status</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <%= if @output_lots == [] do %>
        <tr class="empty-row"><td colspan="5">No output lots recorded.</td></tr>
      <% else %>
        <%= for {ol, idx} <- Enum.with_index(@output_lots, 1) do %>
          <tr>
            <td class="num"><%= idx %></td>
            <td class="mono"><%= ol.lot_code %></td>
            <td class="mono"><%= ol.supplier_batch %></td>
            <td class="num"><%= ol.qty %></td>
            <td><%= ol.status %></td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<%= if @history_photos != [] do %>
<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">
    Chain of custody — <%= length(@history_photos) %> photo<%= if length(@history_photos) == 1, do: "", else: "s" %> · chronological across the whole batch<%= if @history_omitted_count > 0, do: " · #{@history_omitted_count} more captured, see sign-off timestamps", else: "" %>
  </h3>
  <p style="font-size: 8.5pt; color: #666; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
    Every physical movement with a photo, ordered by capture time: goods-in receipt of raw materials, warehouse pickup, pre-production receipt, closeout, output QC, return-pickup, move to finished quarantine.
  </p>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 6px;">
    <%= for p <- @history_photos do %>
      <figure style="margin: 0; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; background: #fafafa;">
        <img src="<%= p.photo_url %>" alt="" style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 130px; object-fit: cover;" />
        <figcaption style="padding: 5px 7px; font-size: 7.5pt; color: #444; line-height: 1.4;">
          <div style="font-weight: 600; color: #111;"><%= p.kind_label %></div>
          <div><%= p.item_name %></div>
          <div style="font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; color: #666;"><%= p.when %></div>
          <div style="color: #666;"><%= p.actor %></div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>
<% end %>

<section>
  <h3 class="section-title">Sign-offs — every MO in the chain + release ceremony</h3>
  <div class="signoff-grid">
    <%= for s <- @signoffs do %>
      <% blank = is_nil(s.name) or s.name == "" or s.name == "—" %>
      <div class="signoff <%= if blank, do: "blank", else: "" %>">
        <div class="role"><%= s.role %></div>
        <div class="name"><%= if blank, do: "—", else: s.name %></div>
        <div class="when"><%= s.when %></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div>Batch Manufacturing Record · <%= @batch_ref %></div>
  <div>Page 1 · Auto-generated <%= @now %></div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
